        <h1 class="h2">Safe and effective for everyone involved</h1>
        <p>We work to support and connect <a href="/find-help/all-service-providers/?location=manchester">many amazing local voluntary organisations</a>, both charities and grassroots groups. Many volunteers offer incredible kindness and generosity to support people who are experiencing homelessness.</p>
        <p>Working with vulnerable adults, some with complex needs, there is a lot to consider when trying to help - from safeguarding of volunteers and those you aim to help, to training, and knowledge about what other support is available (such as the Big Change fund). It is essential that people link into services who can offer advice and long term support to move away from homelessness.</p>
