      <p>Together with <a href="/find-help/organisation/?organisation=coffee4craig">Coffee4Craig</a> and a network of other groups in the city, we have put together some guidance, tools, training and an award scheme to help community led groups to set up and evolve in a way that is safe and effective for everyone involved. You can also join <a href="/manchester/cor/">Coalition of Relief (COR)</a>, a network of Manchester based grassroots organisation. We hope that you find this useful.</p>
